Package it.polimi.ingsw.is25am22new.Model.ComponentTiles

package it.polimi.ingsw.is25am22new.Model.ComponentTiles
  • Class
    Description
    AlienAddon
    AlienAddon represents a specific type of component tile that includes additional functionality for alien presence and specific coloring.
    BatteryComponent
    Represents a specialized component tile in the form of a battery compartment.
    Cabin
    Represents an abstract cabin component tile used in the game.
    Cannon
    The Cannon class represents a specific type of ComponentTile that includes cannon functionality.
    ComponentTile
    Represents a general component tile in a game, which can have various sides with specific functionalities.
    DoubleCannon
    The DoubleCannon class represents a specific type of cannon that extends the functionality of the Cannon base class.
    DoubleEngine
    Represents a specialized type of engine that focuses specifically on the bottom side for activation.
    Engine
    Represents a specific type of component tile called Engine, which can rotate and have an activated engine on one or more sides.
    RegularCabin
    The RegularCabin class is a specific type of cabin that extends the functionality of the Cabin superclass to include support for alien presence management.
    ShieldGenerator
    The ShieldGenerator class represents a shielding component in a system.
    Side
    The Side enum represents the different types of sides a component tile in the game can have.
    SpecialStorageCompartment
    Represents a special type of storage compartment within a component tile.
    StartingCabin
    Represents a specialized type of cabin in the game that serves as the starting point.
    StorageCompartment
    Represents a storage compartment component within a tile that can hold different types of good blocks up to a specified capacity.
    StructuralModule
    The StructuralModule class represents a specialized component tile in the game.
